snippet.title: QuByte Classics: Radical Rex - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
As part of the QuByte Classics series in partnership with Piko Interactive, this compilation brings together both Radical Rex for the MegaDrive / Genesis and its GameBoy predecessor, Baby T-Rex, to the Xbox One (as well as PS4 and Switch).

Radical Rex, Baby T-Rex (C) Piko Interactive
QuByte Classics (C) QuByte Interactive
Xbox One page: https://www.xbox.com/en-ie/games/store/radical-rex-qubyte-classics/9p2dcn2238j5
